<plot>n 2008, Germany got struck by the US mortgage crisis. Especially some managers of numerous Federal State Banks proved to have invested adventurously and unwarrantably. However, the German Federal Banks didn't have to bear any consequences - the State had to stand in. "Financial Crisis" is an entertaining board game, in which you get to play a Federal State Bank. No matter how many imbecile mistakes you make - you always pile up your money. No risk, great fun.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?058682</url></doc>
